 866:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_usart.c ****   *     @arg USART_FLAG_RXNE: Receive data register not empty flag
 867:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_usart.c ****   *     @arg USART_FLAG_IDLE: Idle Line detection flag
 868:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_usart.c ****   *     @arg USART_FLAG_ORE:  OverRun Error flag
